question_text: Which of the following types of learning style do you prefer most while learning? You can only choose one option.
Which of the following types of content do you typically learn more effectively, especially learning a new topic? You can only select up to 3 areas that interest you the most.
What is your highest level of education? You can only choose one option.
Take a look at the popular fields of study below, are you interested in any of them? You can only select up to 3 areas that interest you the most.
